The paper analyzes the evolution of Reddit over time, focusing on user submissions and community attention. This suggests a strong emphasis on social media and online communities (cs.SI), as well as data mining and analysis (cs.SD). The study also involves analyzing the perception and attention of submissions, which could fall under the categories of cybernetics (cs.CY) and computational complexity (cs.CC). Finally, the paper involves analyzing textual content, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR).
